Maybe that person can't start for another two months or something like that.

23
00:01:09.535 --> 00:01:12.660
Discuss, agree, and then select.

24
00:01:12.660 --> 00:01:16.089
And what I'd also like you to do is document the reason

25
00:01:16.089 --> 00:01:19.060
why you selected the particular candidate or why you did

